Reasoning: The paper analyzes news photos using deep learning-based vision APIs, which suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV). The sentiment analysis aspect of the paper could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or information retrieval (cs.IR). The analysis of gender treatment and political candidate portrayal could fall under natural language processing (cs.CL) or cryptography and security (cs.CR) if there are privacy concerns related to the images analyzed.
